-- Barrick Says It Will Assess Implications of Chile Resolution
-- B y   L i e z e l   H i l l
-- 2013-05-24T18:48:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-24/barrick-says-it-will-assess-implications-of-chile-resolution.html
Barrick Gold Corp. (ABX)  said it will
assess the implications of a resolution by Chilean environmental
agency SMA in relation to the company’s Pascua-Lama project in
the Andes.  Barrick said it’s “fully committed” to complying with the
resolution, which includes a fine of about $16 million.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Liezel Hill in Toronto at 
